{"tid":1472563,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［金融抗爭］一人一圖支持Cash Out Challenge","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:36:34.000Z","uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8eb17f6e6d3756d78fd8753c753aefda58e6207","tid":1472563,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpXS2Tt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpXS2Tt.png&h=e1bb3e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7500美金今日攞左出黎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外離岸股票戶口已經ready<br />\n0816或之前就電匯出去買美股<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家多多益善 少少無拘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之一定要攞錢攞美金出黎 或者開離岸戶口電匯走<br />\n<br />\n根據金管局資料 我地銀行體系有6-7成借左去中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔要再幫中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ab2e0c92bf61fcd5d7496a57361b90620910c9","tid":1472563,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>8月15日</strong>：稅局接收工（1200稅務大樓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span